		<td><b>Super game boy adapter for the Snes</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What is the different between the super game boy 2 and regular  Snes adapter ?<br /><br />One says &quot;2&quot; and is blue and has  ?? Connector on the right side and is for the super Famicom console.   The gray case one has no connector on the side and is for the NTSC USA consoles.<br /><br />Is there a technical difference between the 2?  Will the 2 play the game boy color carts?<br /><br /><br />Thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

